description:
Starfield is receiving it's largest update since the launch of the game. The update is arriving May 15th and brings with it new gameplay difficulty options, new features for customizing your ships, detailed surface maps, updates for Xbox Series X Display Settings, and much more.

#starfield #bethesda #gaming

title: Starfield Official May Update Overview

description:
After going hands-on with the new content in SMT V: Vengeance, the dark and twisted RPG is getting even sicker.

Shin Megami Tensei V: Vengeance adds a whole lot more than just quality-of-life improvements and a few gameplay additions. It's one thing to hear Atlus boast about how much it has changed SMT V for the new Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC re-release, but having now played about two hours of a preview demo that focused on the new content, we've seen how Vengeance is building towards something much larger than the original game.

#ShinMegami #ShinMegamiTenseiV #gamespot
title: SMT V: Vengeance Is Much Bigger Than You Think
